headline.print_headline: Castro Hits 2-Run Homer, RBI Double to Lead Astros
headline.main: Castro Hits 2-Run Homer, RBI Double to Lead Astros

lead_paragraph: Jason Castro hit a two-run homer and an RBI double, leading the Houston Astros to a 10-9 victory over a Washington Nationals split-squad Wednesday.
